profile_summary:
As a software engineer, I specialize in creating scalable solutions with Python and tackling complex browser-side challenges with JavaScript. 
In addition to coding, I leverage my experience with batch files to drive automation across various systems. 
You can also find my journey in programming through a multitude of automated projects on various platforms including public repositories on GitHub and other digital showcases. 
When I'm not writing code, I enjoy bringing surreal projects to life like High-on-AI, a surreal image gallery that showcases my passion to code.
